Package: cellSight
Type: Package
Title: Pipeline to facilitate the downstream analysis of single cell experiment
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ranojoy Chatterjee, Chiraag Gohel, Ali Rahnavard
Maintainer: Ranojoy Chatterjee <ranojoy@gwu.edu>, Chiraag Gohel <chiraag@gwu.edu>, Ali Rahnavard <rahnavard@gwu.edu>
Description: The pipeline helps to streamline the downstream analysis of a single cell experiment.
    It does standard filtering and QC plot followed by differential expression using tweedieverse,
    and cell communication using CellChat.
